{"hash":"726c1bd7ad2c12bab26ed7695496c152be95a932","data":{"markdownPage":{"id":"914db715ff9d22fec8ec4c769226194d","title":"Tags","description":"","path":"/bp/tags/","timeToRead":1,"content":"<h1 id=\"tags\"><a href=\"#tags\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Tags</h1>\n<h2 id=\"types\"><a href=\"#types\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Types</h2>\n<h3 id=\"family\"><a href=\"#family\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Family</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Family tags group together entities of a similar nature</p>\n<ul>\n<li>E.G Bosses, Enemies, Quest entities etc</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Tags of this type should be in the form \"family_X\"</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"unique\"><a href=\"#unique\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Unique</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Unique tags are tags added to only one entity at a time</p>\n<ul>\n<li>E.G When randomly picking players</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Tags of this type should be in the form \"unique_X\"</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"initiating\"><a href=\"#initiating\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Initiating</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Initiating tags are tags added once to an entity, after everything has been initiated</li>\n<li>Tags of this type should be in the form \"init_X\"</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"state\"><a href=\"#state\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>State</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>State tags are tags that an entity has while they are in a certain state</p>\n<ul>\n<li>E.G Vehicle upgraded</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Tags of this type should be in the form \"state_X\"</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"other\"><a href=\"#other\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Other</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tags don't fit into the categories above should have clear descriptive names</li>\n</ul>\n","sidebar":"docs","next":"","prev":"/bp/scoreboards/","headings":[{"depth":1,"value":"Tags","anchor":"#tags"},{"depth":2,"value":"Types","anchor":"#types"},{"depth":3,"value":"Family","anchor":"#family"},{"depth":3,"value":"Unique","anchor":"#unique"},{"depth":3,"value":"Initiating","anchor":"#initiating"},{"depth":3,"value":"State","anchor":"#state"},{"depth":3,"value":"Other","anchor":"#other"}],"fileInfo":{"path":"bp/tags.md"}},"allMarkdownPage":{"edges":[{"node":{"path":"/general/animations-and-controllers/","title":"Animations Controllers"}},{"node":{"path":"/bp/tags/","title":"Tags"}},{"node":{"path":"/bp/scoreboards/","title":"Scoreboards"}},{"node":{"path":"/bp/functions/","title":"Functions"}},{"node":{"path":"/bp/entities/","title":"Entities"}},{"node":{"path":"/tools/","title":"Tools"}},{"node":{"path":"/misc/","title":"Misc"}},{"node":{"path":"/intro/","title":"Introduction"}}]}},"context":{}}